{
  "stem": "14900.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So [LAUGHS] I got my little Christmas tree.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She wouldn't permit me to bring in a real one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we were, we were definitely Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But religion, at least at age nine, was not an important thing in my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know what it would have been like had I been older and had different memories.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Various ways, depending on the season-- summer, no school, outdoor play, always in the lumber yard, or playing prison ball, all the physical activities, running in the fields, going out for horse and buggy rides, in the winter, playing indoor games, also outdoors on sleds all winter long, after school.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Played with my dolls, and tea sets, and make believe, lots of painting, lots of artwork.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chinese checkers were very popular.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So were dominoes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What else?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's been a lifetime ago-- checkers, gin rummy, [LAUGHS] and dancing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I learned how to dance when I was about seven, standing on either my father's or one of the cousins' feet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would lead me as we did the waltz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the gramophone was going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a child at that time, when you were dancing and playing games, what were your hopes for the future or dreams?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I always said I was going to work with flowers, always loved flowers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And looking back on it, I must have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because as a mother, after my children had grown, I went back to school and received a floral design degree, along with interior design, space design.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I always knew that it had to be something to do with beauty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The other side of the coin was I'm going to be a doctor like a few of my mother's cousins.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But of course, females did not become doctors then.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
